            Device Lab
          </h1>

          <div class="two-column-text">

            <p>
              The proliferation of platforms (and versions) and the astounding number of devices released makes it more difficult to ensure compatibility and usability of custom software. Our Device Lab with Android, iOS, Lynx, and Windows phones, tablets, laptops, and legacy systems ensure that we have the proper tools to test across devices and platforms. The Device Lab is used to test our mobile, web and software development.
            </p>
            
          </div>

        </article>

      </li>      

      <li class="facilities item">

        <article>

          <img alt="3D Printing and CNC" src="{{theme.link}}/images/facilities/slide-4.jpg" titlke="3D Printing and CNC">

