            3D Printing &amp; CNC
          </h1>

          <div class="two-column-text">

            <p>
              We use 3D printing to prototype small parts and even to produce short runs of internal components. Our collection of 3D printers allow us to print with a variety of materials. We’ve printed with conductive materials to use in fudicials for capacitive touch screens. Our CNC router is used for prototyping small parts in aluminum and cold-rolled steel.
            </p>
            
          </div>

        </article>

      </li>

    </ul>

